sting model with entries kept in individual files along with their comments.&nbsp; This changes things.&nbsp; Once I overcome my irritation at being blind-sided and having some of my archiving corrupted as part of this change, I will be able to see the advantages of this approach for scaling into article form, repurposing blog content and so on.&nbsp; But for now, the throwback, flashback, and related experimentation is at an end.]<br>
